name: Patricia Alexandra Orleans
description:
& K Y E P – patriciabhaby
I am 100 romantic. Tender, sweet and loving. I am not the tough kind of girl, I am fragile but passionate, I can roll on the floor laughing, yet I know how to be serious at moments. I am very eager to start a family of my own, to be a responsible wife, to take care of my hubby and make him the happiest person in this world… Do you want to apply for that position?
